@startuml
title Course Addition – Component Overview

skinparam componentStyle rectangle

actor "Course Author" as Author

package "Minimal Course Files" as Files {
    [course.json\n//Title + Hole Info//\n(Course Info optional)] as JSON
    [course.tscn\n//3D Scene//] as TSCN
}

package "Course Selector" as Selector {
    [CourseList\ncourse_list.gd] as CL
    [CourseSelector\ncourse_selector.gd] as CS
}

[SceneManager\nscene_manager.gd] as SM

note bottom of JSON
  Defaults applied when
  Course Info is missing:
  • Tee Colors
  • Texture Indices
end note

Author --> JSON : create
Author --> TSCN : create

CL --> JSON : parse & validate
CL --> TSCN : check exists

CS --> CL : discover courses\nget_course_info()\nget_hole_info()
CS --> SM : change_scene()
SM --> TSCN : load

@enduml
